channel.title: Can't run any clients! Launcher error! please help!
channel.description:
[center]So I can't run any desktop clients because I keep getting this error...
[IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/fm0wb5.jpg[/img]
Okay, So I've tried as much as I could, researched as much as I could and I just CAN'T figure it out. I'm running Windows Vista, 64bit, I've tried running clients with both the (x86) and without, I'm apparently getting an error saying can't find launcher...
[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/fng5ya.jpg[/img]
And I can't compile either..
[IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/25yx8o5.jpg[/img]
98 errors??..I just don't understand what is going on here..I've also messed with class paths and stuff..I have those all right..but I don't understand what is going wrong..if anybody could help in anyway it would be GREAT....Thanks.[/Center]
